{"tid":1361333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[極致左膠］用愛對抗暴力","createTime":"2019-07-24T14:46:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T13:05:14.000Z","uid":92790,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"abff98a4d65882b081e962ce66d192f7e266cd79","tid":1361333,"uid":92790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:47:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">讓愛光復元朗 愛護藍絲鄉民</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://youtu.be/4zNaEukzyGk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4zNaEukzyGk&h=b21f8491&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4zNaEukzyGk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4zNaEukzyGk&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0B%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=e2f87f5a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4zNaEukzyGk</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n抗爭運動去到依一刻 所有既說話都已經失效<br />\n我地再點譴責政府 譴責警察 譴責鄉黑 譴責中聯辦<br />\n佢地都可以<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">視若無睹</span></span><br />\n我地既訊求 一個都冇理<br />\n<br />\n相反<br />\n局勢不斷先級 人民斗人民 最後可能以命換命<br />\n<br />\n對外 比中國更多理由 干預香港內政 <br />\n未必係解放軍 可能係其他有創意既方法<br />\n（雖然就算冇理由 中共都可以捏造事實）<br />\n<br />\n對內 令到抗爭運動 面對更大壓力<br />\n<br />\n所以 我地依一刻最需要 唔係以暴易暴 而係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">用和理非做矛 由勇武派做盾</span></span><br />\n實現人民內部大和解 進一步擴大民眾基礎<br />\n<br />\n雖然焦土真係好爽 但我地係有一d價值需要<span style=\"color: red;\">守護</span><br />\n係焦土之前 可唔可以有一次 <span style=\"color: red;\">用愛去對抗暴力</span><br />\n<br />\n老實講 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">愛</span></span>真係極度左膠<br />\n但係 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">愛</span></span>  <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係唔會有人唔鍾意</span></span><br />\n<br />\n鄉民（切割黑社會）保家衛族，係出於對家園既<span style=\"color: red;\">愛</span><br />\n佢地當初以愛之名行使暴力，我地就可以用愛同非黑既鄉民connect，鼓勵大家愛護香港，守護香港，唔好比中聯辦繼續發起恐襲，甚至借元朗恐襲之名，進以比解放軍入城，屠殺平民<br />\n<br />\n唔單止普通鄉民，我地仲要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">connect藍絲</span></span>，比佢地感受到我地對香港既愛。我地要對話，不斷既對話。好似唐僧咁樣，永遠好脾氣咁循循善誘。唔好因爲任何無理回應而放棄，亦唔好比佢地塞埋自己對耳。目標唔係要佢地buy我地，而係明白我地做既一切係出於<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">愛</span></span><br />\n<br />\n上面全部都係理想主義<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">發夢都唔會發生</span></span><br />\n<br />\n但係愛既正當性 尤其是面對暴力既時候 係最大<br />\n鄉民唔可以再話我地挑釁<br />\n政府唔可以再話我地係政見之爭<br />\n再有遊行人士受傷 就只可以係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">恐襲</span><br />\n<br />\n打到依到 我都覺得自己膠到爆<br />\n但我真係好想見到<br />\n727 係一大堆既紅色心心&hearts;️&hearts;️&hearts;️<br />\n而唔係有人受傷流血<br />\n<br />\n利申 <br />\n冷氣軍師<br />\n剩係出過616 但會出727"},{"pid":"24e9c7f3c9d36593a6d3ed1c56ef48bf47c2e25e","tid":1361333,"uid":92790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:51:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f4c960e68e5d5cbf358548ace80a716f1ad3fbf","tid":1361333,"uid":92790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:54:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8bb2d5908394e65c18cb4bd61d2ee5aff86fb166","tid":1361333,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:55:08.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"465e42e6acc0cffd16a2ea9c8d256aa8137f5ac8","tid":1361333,"uid":92790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:57:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d204edc0080755b928b306cfc77c151424e1dcf","tid":1361333,"uid":92790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:01:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a184b98b59d97a8b2fd2b6167da8bba63c4df592","tid":1361333,"uid":92790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:12:02.000Z","msg":"太膠冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c35e364faa224d127792616f5d88bd54abc18c14","tid":1361333,"uid":92790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:19:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6c1d06e4c215a19bf08a97d7097cef6f6cc3e2c","tid":1361333,"uid":92790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:19:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8e15fbb2be2bbf16f05edea45856797a27db91d","tid":1361333,"uid":92790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:19:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f87ac685d018fbd9ff1141126aa201943089e28","tid":1361333,"uid":92790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:19:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"374ee6367b42820d9e4953faba0784d7ec3ca69b","tid":1361333,"uid":92790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:20:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15d15aa1d0983d2b2cd28e34404923a62ff97c37","tid":1361333,"uid":92790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:20:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1467c62f5b2745d001faaf9f57464cd687aaadb","tid":1361333,"uid":92790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:20:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a32946b327f0b72f098af53f0ef00328fe74adcd","tid":1361333,"uid":92790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:20:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"150d51a6e4b6c84eb9b372e5ae64b96c841168eb","tid":1361333,"uid":92790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T